@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fpxdwi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v2 - (wp.sin(v1 + 0.57) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.84)))
    v2 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.75 + tmp + 0.91) + wp.sin(v1 + 0.10)))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
